border, and the Turks warned the

14:07.814 --> 14:12.051 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Russians about that. It seems to
be the last straw for the Turks.

14:12.085 --> 14:15.121 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
There are some people who are
saying the Turks should have

14:15.154 --> 14:17.623 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
