14:20.693 --> 14:24.363 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Russians. And as a NATO ally,
it's very important that the

14:24.397 --> 14:27.166 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
United States defend this right
that every country's border are

14:27.200 --> 14:30.803 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
sacrosanct. And what the
Russians did is clearly illegal

14:30.837 --> 14:32.805 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
under international law. JUDY
WOODRUFF: So, Angela Stent, if

14:32.839 --> 14:37.076 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
