accomplish by having done this?

14:44.817 --> 14:47.386 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
ANGELA STENT: Well, I think the
Turks, they disagree with the

14:47.420 --> 14:50.456 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
