to happen -- and Angela is

16:05.832 --> 16:08.968 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
absolutely correct about this --
is, it's a crowded airspace in a

16:09.001 --> 16:12.872 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
very small country. You have
American, French, sometimes

16:12.905 --> 16:16.876 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Arab, Russian aircraft and
Turkish aircraft patrolling in a

16:16.909 --> 16:21.480 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
