be conducting combat operations

16:28.254 --> 16:31.791 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
is critical. The U.S. and Russia
have begun to do that under

16:31.824 --> 16:34.227 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
