see that as a provocative

17:03.256 --> 17:05.424 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
offense? ANGELA STENT: Well, I
think the Russians, they are

17:05.458 --> 17:08.928 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
