to them. And they really want to

17:17.803 --> 17:21.073 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
be -- they want the U.S. to come
to them and they want this broad

17:21.107 --> 17:23.843 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
coalition. They want to be the
leader. And so they're really

17:23.876 --> 17:26.112 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
