Burns, is -- do you sense,

19:44.850 --> 19:48.554 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
though, that there are still
efforts to bring the Russians

19:48.587 --> 19:51.957 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
around? I mean, I keep reading
reports that the administration

19:51.991 --> 19:54.860 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
continues to work on that, but
we just haven't seen any sign of

19:54.894 --> 19:58.364 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
it yet. NICHOLAS BURNS: Well, we
need to work with the Russians,

19:58.397 --> 20:00.933 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
